$ System.Net.FtpWebRequest

`System.Net.FtpWebRequest` derives from → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Net/WebRequest[`WebRequest`] (as also does
→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Net/HttpWebRequest[`System.Net.HttpWebRequest`]).

Microsoft → https://github.com/dotnet/platform-compat/blob/master/docs/DE0003.md[recommends not to use `FtpWebRequest`] for new development and
refers to a → https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1371964/free-ftp-library[this StackOverflow thred] for alternatives. The answer with the
most upvotes condiders → https://github.com/robinrodricks/FluentFTP[FluentFTP] (MIT licence) as an alternative.
